Class GymOwnerService

java.lang.Object
com.flipkart.business.GymOwnerService
All Implemented Interfaces:
GymOwnerInterface
public class GymOwnerService extends Object implements GymOwnerInterface
GymOwnerService provides the implementation of GymOwnerInterface, allowing gym owners to manage their gyms, view gyms, validate credentials, and update their information.
